text: Christian Busch (8 January 1880 - 30 March 1977) was a German gymnast. He competed in three events at the 1904 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1880 births Category:1977 deaths Category:German male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Germany Category:Gymnasts at the 1904 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Wuppertal
